---
// TrustSection — verified memory trust signals
---

<section class="section">
  <div class="section-head">
    <div><div class="kicker">Trust</div><h2>Separate verified memory from raw submissions.</h2></div>
    <p>Open memory only works when users can see what is trusted. Public pages should highlight verified cases and keep low-evidence auto-imported memories out of the main path.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="strip">
    <article class="card"><small>Verified</small><h3>Evidence required</h3><p>Verified fixes need a root cause, a fastest verification step, and proof that the fix works.</p></article>
    <article class="card"><small>Private data</small><h3>No secrets or source dumps</h3><p>Cases should summarize failures. Do not submit credentials, customer data, or proprietary code.</p></article>
    <article class="card"><small>Poisoning control</small><h3>Agents must verify locally</h3><p>Memory results are guidance, not truth. Agents should still check current runtime state before acting.</p></article>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .section { padding: 76px 0; border-top: 1px solid var(--line); }

  .section-head {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(0, .78fr) minmax(320px, 1fr);
    gap: 58px;
    align-items: start;
    margin-bottom: 36px;
  }

  .kicker { color: var(--accent); font-size: 12px; font-weight: 800; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 11px; }
  h2 { margin: 0; font-size: 36px; line-height: 1.16; font-weight: 780; }
  .section-head p { margin: 0; color: var(--muted); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.84; }

  .strip {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
    gap: 18px;
  }

  .card {
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #fff, var(--surface-2));
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 26px;
  }

  .card small { display: block; color: var(--faint); font-size: 12px; margin-bottom: 15px; }
  .card h3 { margin: 0 0 11px; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.32; }
  .card p { margin: 0; color: var(--muted); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.74; }

  @media (max-width: 980px) {
    .section-head { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    h2 { font-size: 32px; }
    .strip { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .section { padding: 58px 0; }
    h2 { font-size: 29px; }
    .card { padding: 22px; }
  }
</style>
